      <title>皇家加勒比邮轮公司股价上涨，邮轮需求增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/royal-caribbean-s-outlook-falls-short-on-hurricane-milton-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家加勒比游轮有限公司 (Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.) 股价飙升至历史新高，此前该游轮运营商今年第四次上调了盈利预期，并表示预计强劲需求将持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/royal-caribbean-s-outlook-falls-short-on-hurricane-milton-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
